Title: Fulfillment
Description: Guarantees fulfillment in time with the conditions stipulated in the contract.

Title: Prepaid
Description: Guarantee by which the supplier requests a prepayment from the procuring entity.

Title: Latent defects
Description: Guarantee on the possible defects that a good may have that are not discoverable through general inspection at the time of delivery.

Title: Confidentiality
Description: Guarantee that commits the supplier to safeguard the confidential information that has been granted.

Title: Quality
Description: Commitment from the supplier to deliver the goods and services in the quality specified in the contract.
